64
00:21:11,234 --> 00:21:39,301
while protecting homeowners and while protecting the retirement incomes of seniors in our community, to increase tenant protections, to increase the city's ability to connect displaced tenants with new comparable affordable housing, to make sure that relocation payments, compensation to displaced tenants aligns with the true cost of moving within our community, and to increase the incentives and the assistance to owners or condo developers

65
00:21:39,888 --> 00:21:42,090
to help with finding new housing for their tenants.

66
00:21:45,412 --> 00:21:55,480
